3) Value chain study in the gold sector in Mali ("Le rapport de l’etude sur l’identification des acteurs de la chaine de valeur Or");
4) SFNS report on health behaviour in the natural stone sector in India;
5) Demo of safe practice at Cobble Yard Premises in the natural stone sector in India
